    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## 2. Bouncing Ball \u2014 Multiple Bounces\n\nTo simulate repeated bounces, we use the stateful API: `np_cvode_create` builds a persistent integrator, `np_cvode_step` advances it segment-by-segment, and `np_cvode_reinit` resets the state after each impact (reversing the velocity with coefficient of restitution $e = 0.8$). Reusing one handle across all bounces avoids the cost of rebuilding the linear solver and re-registering events on each segment.\n\nWe also pass `rootdir = [-1]` so CVODE only detects falling crossings of $h$. Without this, the post-bounce state $h = 0,\\ v > 0$ sits exactly on the event surface and would re-trigger immediately.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Multi-bounce via stateful CVODE handle.\n   rootdir = [-1] only fires on falling crossings of bh, so the post-bounce\n   state (bh = 0, bv > 0) doesn't immediately re-trigger the root. */\ncor : 0.8$\nt_end : 8.0$\ndt : 0.01$\n\nt_all : [0.0]$  h_all : [10.0]$  v_all : [0.0]$\nevent_times : []$\n\nsolver : np_cvode_create([bv, -g], [bt, bh, bv],\n                         [10.0, 0.0], 0.0,\n                         1e-12, 1e-12, adams, [bh], 5000, [-1])$\n\nt_now : 0.0$\nwhile t_now < t_end do block([res, ev],\n  res : np_cvode_step(solver, min(t_now + dt, t_end)),\n  if length(res[3]) > 0 then (\n    /* An event fired during this step.  Record the event point and\n       reinit; the integrator continued past the event to res[1]\n       without knowing about the bounce, so we discard that state. */\n    ev : first(res[3]),\n    event_times : endcons(ev[1], event_times),\n    t_now : ev[1],\n    t_all : endcons(ev[1], t_all),\n    h_all : endcons(ev[2][1], h_all),\n    v_all : endcons(ev[2][2], v_all),\n    np_cvode_reinit(solver, ev[1], [0.0, -cor * ev[2][2]])\n  ) else (\n    t_now : res[1],\n    t_all : endcons(res[1], t_all),\n    h_all : endcons(res[2][1], h_all),\n    v_all : endcons(res[2][2], v_all)\n  )\n)$\n\nprintf(true, \"~d bounces detected~%\", length(event_times))$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "ax_draw2d(\n  color=\"#2563eb\", line_width=1.5,\n  lines(t_all, h_all),\n  title=\"Bouncing Ball with Restitution (e=0.8)\",\n  xlabel=\"t (s)\", ylabel=\"h (m)\",\n  grid=true\n)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## 3. Projectile with Drag \u2014 Target Altitude\n\nA projectile launched upward with quadratic air drag:\n$$\\dot{h} = v, \\quad \\dot{v} = -g - \\frac{\\rho\\,C_d\\,A}{2m}\\,v\\,|v|$$\n\nEvents: detect when the projectile crosses $h = 50\\,$m (ascending and descending).",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "/* Physical parameters */\nmass : 1.0$    /* kg */\nCd : 0.47$     /* drag coefficient (sphere) */\nAcs : 0.01$    /* cross-section area m^2 */\nrho : 1.225$   /* air density kg/m^3 */\ndrag_coeff : rho * Cd * Acs / (2 * mass)$\n\n/* v*abs(v) for correct drag direction */\ntspan3 : np_linspace(0.0, 12.0, 600)$\n\n[traj3, events3] : np_cvode(\n    [pv, -g - drag_coeff * pv * abs(pv)],\n    [pt, ph, pv], [0.0, 50.0], tspan3,\n    1e-10, 1e-10, adams, [ph - 50.0])$\n\nprintf(true, \"Events at h=50m:~%\")$\nfor ev in events3 do\n  printf(true, \"  t = ~,4f s, h = ~,4f m, v = ~,4f m/s~%\",\n         first(ev), second(ev)[1], second(ev)[2])$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 6,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "Events at h=50m:\no149  t = 1.2329 s, h = 50.0000 m, v = 31.9721 m/s\no149  t = 7.3296 s, h = 50.0000 m, v = -28.0417 m/s\no149$$\\mathbf{done}$$\nfalse"
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "t3 : np_slice(traj3, all, 0)$\nh3 : np_slice(traj3, all, 1)$\n\nev_t3 : map(first, events3)$\nev_h3 : map(lambda([e], second(e)[1]), events3)$\n\nax_draw2d(\n  color=\"#2563eb\", line_width=2, name=\"h(t)\",\n  lines(t3, h3),\n  color=\"#dc2626\", marker_size=8, name=\"h=50m crossings\",\n  points(ev_t3, ev_h3),\n  color=\"#9ca3af\", dash=\"dash\",\n  explicit(50, t, 0, 12),\n  title=\"Projectile with Drag\",\n  xlabel=\"t (s)\", ylabel=\"h (m)\",\n  grid=true, showlegend=true\n)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 7,
      "outputs": [
        {
